-80 -90 -85 -95
AEFHKT AB CD 0
stand stand female 4000
AHMV ABCDEFGHIJK medium unknown
#8501
Bateau man~
Bateau~
Bateau points his Jericho 942FS handgun at your head.
~
Bateau, like Motoko, is an expert in unlawful activities, and has
been her partner for several years. His main role is to control and
support Motoko who usually tends to go too far. They have been
working together so long that they have grown accustomed to
each other.
~
Human~
