AHMV ABCDEFGHIJK medium unknown
#8503
aramaki man~
Aramaki~
Aramaki, head of Section 9, watches the study of the Puppet Master here.
~
Chief Aramaki is both intelligent and resourceful... he has to be to 
control the "unique" personalities of Section 9 (Mainly Kusanagi and 
Bateau). As for how long he has been the chief, no one can remember 
when he wasn't. He is a very straight forward person, and does what 
it takes to get a job done.
~
Human~
