AHMV ABCDEFGHIJK medium unknown
#8504
ishikawa man~
Ishikawa~
Ishikawa hacks into databases looking for information here.
~
Ishikawa is the oldest member of Section 9 next to Aramaki. He is relied 
upon to keep cool in a crisis and help the team to remain focused.
~
Human~
