#8550
The Emergency Room~
Wounded lying on beds, moan their pains to green coated Doctors here. The 
sound of machine blips fill you ears as those machines monitor the state 
of those moaning patients. The faint smells of chemicals, and gore fills 
your nostrils, making you a bit queasy. There are a few burly orderlies 
keeping the peace in this room, making you feel as if nothing can threaten 
you.
~
